<LP>
   FRESNO, Calif. -- WestAir Holding Inc. said it realigned
some routes flown by its United Express airline unit. That
move includes the addition of new service and the suspension
of other service that will entail furloughing pilots and
other personnel.
   Among the changes, WestAir said it plans to begin service
Oct. 15 between Dulles airport outside Washington, D.C., and
