but also get to say how much revenue this will "raise"
(lose).
   To add insult to injury, Republicans will tell us they
didn't "raise rates," but only adopted a "surcharge." Voters
will have to figure out for themselves that a 20% surcharge
is the same as a boost in the marginal rate, perhaps a
substantial one depending on details.
